      • isMultiSession

        public boolean isMultiSession()
        Check if Aspera Transfer should use all available connections to the Aspera Service. If set the remote_host field on the transfer spec is updated with a suffix '-all' on the subdomain and will direct the underlying Aspera SDK to use multiple sessions for a transfer. Default is false
